                              Product Description
======================================================================================

 After the support of Ferry Corsten, Markus Schulz, Armin van Buuren, Sander van Doorn, and the awesome feedback of all trance family around the world on Dr. Kucho!'s previous tracks "To Russia With Love" and "Hale Bopp", he decided to make this album which is a tribute to the real progressive/trance music that makes your mind travel away by telling a story rather than filling the spectrum with noisy sounds.
 Dr. Kucho! took this opportunity to create Journey Tunes, his own new label focused on melodic trance and progressive house music. We are going to bring back the beautiful music! Because if you are not part of the solution, you are part of the problem!
